+ [`qrels.adhoc.351-400.txt`](../src/main/resources/topics-and-qrels/qrels.adhoc.351-400.txt): [qrels for TREC-7 Ad Hoc Topics 351-400](http://trec.nist.gov/data/qrels_eng/)
